,"msg":"我想知如果口罩外面有d 有病毒既飛沬<br />\n會唔會穿過口罩入你身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1c95c418169135fd7adf396a67813c2072dc15","tid":1835261,"uid":295602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e98090e3df0e668189d2854b25e6a591311a0ab","tid":1835261,"uid":5725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T20:38:28.000Z","msg":"我想知如果口罩外面有d 有病毒既飛沬<br />\n會唔會穿過口罩入你身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T20:45:47.000Z","msg":"簡單咁講就係你唔直接掂到就冇事<br />\n本身啲菌同病毒就trap左係飛沫度，當係一個vector/medium咁傳播<br />\n<br />\n手術口罩本身有隔水層擋著飛沫<br />\n其實細菌病毒又未有咁恐怖識自己郁穿過口罩嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除非隻武漢肺炎係空氣傳播 咁預冚球剷啦"},{"pid":"bc5507516a3ae1b3bd19e33d735aa7c575324555","tid":1835261,"uid":276558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T20:46:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n命就得一條<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3061e4db847f13ed6e92279dbbb993bcaaa602","tid":1835261,"uid":189652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T20:51:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a3d43ce50ceac914358d4dc29cec1020a6c5ef9","tid":1835261,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:01:38.000Z","msg":"ching識吾識㗎😅 口罩=萬能㗎，連病毒都擋到㗎喎😅 唔識咪亂噏啦🤭"},{"pid":"6fe9178783ad1c89e4a6e04896628fce0835ff98","tid":1835261,"uid":92145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:12:05.000Z","msg":"空氣傳播唔係四隻字咁簡單<br />\n要睇埋可以係咩環境下以幾多時間傳播等等做參考<br />\n冇人講過口罩係100%防到<br />\n但肯定唔戴=中門大開"},{"pid":"a2a7ecb3c617686d00488af142cc63a4e88d6a5e","tid":1835261,"uid":266100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:48:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}